1. Add support of appPackage and appActivity parameters for Android devices (reading from a .properties file and then
setting in the DesiredCapabilities). Locally installed Appium DT has no need in these parameters, but for Appium server
of Minsk Mobile Farm it’s mandatory.
Done. Required fields and initialization for those are added to Driver.class.
Driver URL was pointed to the mobileFarm url with a personal token.

